{"tid":840078,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國國台辦：台灣應立即停止對中國大陸滲透","createTime":"2018-09-28T12:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T14:56:48.000Z","uid":144372,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"12acaa119cacca5ef124534048e8f90a8c5fcb4f","tid":840078,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:06:45.000Z","msg":"大陸中央電視台昨天(15號)在新聞聯播和「焦點訪談」節目中，披露台灣對大陸進行情報工作，並舉出三個案例，透過色誘、金錢往來等方式，在台灣吸收來台讀書、交流的陸生。<br />\n<br />\n根據新華社報導，大陸國台辦安峰山今天(16號)表示，據向有關部門了解，一段時期以來，台灣間諜情報機關以大陸為目標，大肆加強情報竊取和滲透破壞活動，為此國家安全機關組織開展專項打擊行動，陸方要求台灣有關方面立即停止對大陸的滲透破壞活動，避免對日益複雜嚴峻的兩岸關係造成進一步傷害。(資料照片)<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/國台辦-台灣應立即停止對大陸滲透-032613322.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%B0%E8%BE%A6-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%87%89%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%B3%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E5%B0%8D%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E6%BB%B2%E9%80%8F-032613322.html&d=ReGn24TEQ5kiF2pOKDudcosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=dff9848c\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/國台辦-台灣應立即停止對大陸滲透-032613322.html</a>"},{"pid":"705ec210e547fd799fafe203212912684340e659","tid":840078,"uid":57214,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:09:04.000Z","msg":"角色倒轉咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9930b7b2886252c44d1eaaae30ec1ce230132388","tid":840078,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:11:53.000Z","msg":"一年準備、二年反攻、三年掃蕩、五年成功"},{"pid":"b4b691c7a492fc31c1d7458e327ccfc7b393bcbc","tid":840078,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:19:47.000Z","msg":"又話台灣係中國一部份？"},{"pid":"c56729bbb814284c1f9b1f9555c84063ffb23cad","tid":840078,"uid":140309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b4b691c7a492fc31c1d7458e327ccfc7b393bcbc","tid":840078,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:19:47.000Z","msg":"又話台灣係中國一部份？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018